          <title>New Google Chrome Split-Screen Feature Leaked in Beta Build - Exclusive Update for Web Browser Lovers</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A new split-screen feature has been discovered in a Google Chrome Canary beta build, offering users the ability to use two windows within a single tab. The functionality is not yet live for regular users but shows promise for enhanced productivity and customization options.]]></description>
